\mt1 Esther
\is1 Introduction
\ip This document, migpangguhud concerning the sabeka Hudiyu named ki Istir. Neyitabu this dengan of timpu si King Aswiru pad the migmandu there to inged named of Pirsya. Neyimu si Istir rayna of King Aswiru liwan ki Rayna Basti of migsupak kandin. Ne due also sabeka person named ki Haman egkeupian eggule of Jews, but pinaahi of kabulut of Istir and of love rin of me karumaan din, nekeisip sikandin egpangabangan din the me karumaan din so that not sikandan egpatey.
\ip Nahuhud again here the kaligkatan of sahakeen of Jews named dan of Purim. Te sika sahakeen, egsumsumanen of Jews ke immenu sikandan of saved of God ligkat of enemy dan si Haman.
\iot Main components of this “book”
\io1 The pegkeyimu of Istir rayna \ior 1:1–2:23\ior*
\io1 The peglelalis of Haman \ior 3:1–5:14\ior*
\io1 The killing ki Haman \ior 6:1–7:10\ior*
\io1 The pegpangimatey of Jews of enemies dan \ior 8:1–10:3\ior*
